com.github.rmielnik.list

Interface ViewHolderFactory<T extends RecyclerItem>

  • Type Parameters:
    T -

    is a class that implements interface RecyclerItem or an interface that extends interface RecyclerItem.

    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ViewHolderFactoryRegistry

    public ViewHolderFactory<T extends RecyclerItem>

    Represents object that is able to create class AbstractViewHolder or class AbstractUpdatableViewHolder for given RecyclerItem.viewHolderType.

    See Also:
    class AbstractViewHolder, class AbstractUpdatableViewHolder, RecyclerItem.viewHolderType
